lio"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T02:25:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.oaktreecapital.com/insights/howard-marks-memos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oaktreecapital.com%2Finsights%2Fhoward-marks-memos&d=h8K6dYNnEA4rSgnLcindhcLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=df254981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.oaktreecapital.com/insights/howard-marks-memos</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zh3zv4r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZh3zv4r.jpg&h=edb7b082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCapital Market Line<br />\n<br />\nOaktree memo , coming into focus"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"咁應該係佢用字搞錯咗<br />\n因為CML同SML係兩樣嘢嚟<br />\n<br />\nCML喺Markowitz model已經會出現<br />\n其實就係加咗risk-free asset落個market之後嘅efficient frontier<br />\n線上面任何一點都係market portfolio同risk-free asset組合而成嘅portfolio<br />\n<br />\n而SML係講緊每隻asset佢地嘅(excess) return同(systematic) risk之間嘅關係<br />\n呢度嘅risk通常都係指beta<br />\n即係要under CAPM嘅framework先會derive到出嚟"},{"pid":"317242928257d131a0322d687c7ecc8d2847efa3","tid":2348651,"uid":297770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef57eea40d6664553b7693b0a8cabbc800485e47","tid":2348651,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5e26dca33df873cf633303ca834aa559952e3cf","tid":2348651,"uid":297770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T02:01:21.000Z","msg":"新年快樂呀，要注意身子呀大夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"劏到仆街 而家一笑就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"啪返幾粒神曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3095164b470e31534aad4736815b02660704ac","tid":2348651,"uid":230549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40588038d6033583c5a3e809a8cda467ed84ce12","tid":2348651,"uid":136590,"like":3,"dislik